    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "speakerNameEn": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――月出高等学校学園祭当日、腹筋カフェにて",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 0.8,
      "endTime": 2.5999999206,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_wind-03.m4a",
          "delay": 433.3333333
        },
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_wind-03.m4a",
          "delay": 866.6666667000001
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_schoolclass-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "schoolclass-00-noon",
      "startTime": 1.2666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_schoolclass-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "schoolclass-00-noon",
      "startTime": 2.6666667302
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai Komiyama",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2510_01_05/sud_vo_adv_event_2510_01_05-ai001.m4a",
      "text": "ようこそ！　未来のシックスパックさん達！\nさぁ、腹筋に愛を籠めますよ～！　ムキムキムンッ！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 2.6666667302,
      "endTime": 12.593333276100001,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_schoolclass-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "schoolclass-00-noon",
      "startTime": 6.6666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_schoolclass-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "schoolclass-00-noon",
      "startTime": 11.6333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_schoolclass-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "schoolclass-00-noon",
      "startTime": 12.7943081856
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono Nagase",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2510_01_05/sud_vo_adv_event_2510_01_05-ktn001.m4a",
      "text": "そんな萌え萌えキュンみたいに言わなくても……\n腹筋カフェって愛とトレーニングするカフェだったのね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 12.7943081856,
      "endTime": 20.954308319099997,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_paper-01.m4a",
          "delay": 8450.4085858
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa Ibuki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2510_01_05/sud_vo_adv_event_2510_01_05-ngs001.m4a",
      "text": "結構フードとドリンクも種類があるね\n激辛プロテインカレーにプロテインたこ焼き……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 21.3886168162,
      "endTime": 29.3876410166,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_chime-04.m4a",
          "delay": 16511.3831838
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_schoolclass-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "schoolclass-00-noon",
      "startTime": 29.588615926
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono Nagase",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2510_01_05/sud_vo_adv_event_2510_01_05-ktn002.m4a",
      "text": "全部プロテインじゃない……でもみんな美味しそうに\n食べてるわね……私達も試食してみてもいいかも――",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 29.588615926,
      "endTime": 38.5384810765,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yuu Suzumura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2510_01_05/sud_vo_adv_event_2510_01_05-yu001.m4a",
      "text": "星見高等学校からお越しの星見プロの長瀬琴乃さん！\n伊吹渚さん！　大至急、生徒会室までお越し下さい！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 40.3061178207,
      "endTime": 50.0050970077,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_zawa-02.m4a",
          "delay": 11293.877347299996
        },
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_zawa-02.m4a",
          "delay": 19060.544013999996
        },
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_zawa-02.m4a",
          "delay": 26719.882011399997
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_schoolclass-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "schoolclass-00-noon",
      "startTime": 45.122274208
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_schoolclass-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "schoolclass-00-noon",
      "startTime": 50.2061175664
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono Nagase",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2510_01_05/sud_vo_adv_event_2510_01_05-ktn003.m4a",
      "text": "ちょっ、今の優よね！？　校内放送で\nあんな風に私達の名前を呼んだら……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 50.2061175664,
      "endTime": 56.5394532522,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_schoolclass-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "schoolclass-00-noon",
      "startTime": 56.7404281617
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa Ibuki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2510_01_05/sud_vo_adv_event_2510_01_05-ngs002.m4a",
      "text": "わわわ、みんな私達に気付いたみたい！？\n早く生徒会室に向かわないとだけど、どこにあるの！？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 56.7404281617,
      "endTime": 64.88238048560001,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_run-in-single-02.m4a",
          "delay": 11292.911020900001
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_schoolclass-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "schoolclass-00-noon",
      "startTime": 65.0666730245
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai Komiyama",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2510_01_05/sud_vo_adv_event_2510_01_05-ai002.m4a",
      "text": "生徒会室はこの廊下を直進です！　走れ～",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 65.0666730245,
      "endTime": 69.1333417257,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_schoolclass-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "schoolclass-00-noon",
      "startTime": 67.6666725159
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_studentcouncilroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "seitokai",
      "startTime": 70.2333417257
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono Nagase",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2510_01_05/sud_vo_adv_event_2510_01_05-ktn004.m4a",
      "text": "はあ……はあ……ちょっと優！　あの放送は何！？\n校内の人達に私達が来ていることがバレて大変――",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 71.3014154118,
      "endTime": 81.2014150303,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_studentcouncilroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "seitokai",
      "startTime": 74.4333391826
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_studentcouncilroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "seitokai",
      "startTime": 81.2023899397
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yuu Suzumura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2510_01_05/sud_vo_adv_event_2510_01_05-yu002.m4a",
      "text": "ごめんなぁぁ……でもこっちも切羽詰まっとんねん！\n二人ともうちらと一緒にミュージカルに出てくれへん？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 81.2023899397,
      "endTime": 90.2282667478,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_studentcouncilroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "seitokai",
      "startTime": 90.435727342
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono Nagase",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2510_01_05/sud_vo_adv_event_2510_01_05-ktn005.m4a",
      "text": "みゅ、ミュージカルに！？　そんな急に言われても……\nとりあえず事情を説明してくれるかしら",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 90.435727342,
      "endTime": 98.9481764158,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_studentcouncilroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "seitokai",
      "startTime": 99.1491513253
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui Tendo",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2510_01_05/sud_vo_adv_event_2510_01_05-rui001.m4a",
      "text": "実は昨日、学園祭の決起集会を生徒会で開いたの\n私達は仕事で行けなかったのだけれど……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 99.1491513253,
      "endTime": 107.85413961420001,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_studentcouncilroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "seitokai",
      "startTime": 108.0551145237
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yuu Suzumura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2510_01_05/sud_vo_adv_event_2510_01_05-yu003.m4a",
      "text": "生徒会のみんな、食べ過ぎてもうたみたいで……\n酷い胃もたれになって今日休んでしまったんです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 108.0551145237,
      "endTime": 116.3908963841,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yuu Suzumura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2510_01_05/sud_vo_adv_event_2510_01_05-yu004.m4a",
      "text": "生徒会メンバーに任せとった敵役がおらんと全校生徒が\n楽しみにしとったミュージカルが中止になってしまう",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 116.588447857,
      "endTime": 124.9459305764,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_studentcouncilroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "seitokai",
      "startTime": 125.1551145237
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yuu Suzumura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2510_01_05/sud_vo_adv_event_2510_01_05-yu005.m4a",
      "text": "ずばり、二人には敵役の悪魔をやってほしいんよ！\nお願いしますっ！　うちらのために一肌脱いで下さい",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 125.1551145237,
      "endTime": 133.8764096898,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_studentcouncilroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "seitokai",
      "startTime": 134.0884509088
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono Nagase",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2510_01_05/sud_vo_adv_event_2510_01_05-ktn006.m4a",
      "text": "じ、事情は分かったけど敵役って……\n付け焼刃じゃ難しいと思うのだけれど……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 134.0884509088,
      "endTime": 141.6242783548,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_studentcouncilroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "seitokai",
      "startTime": 141.8252532643
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui Tendo",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2510_01_05/sud_vo_adv_event_2510_01_05-rui002.m4a",
      "text": "もし恋に出演した渚と、不思議の国のアリスの劇で\n優と共演した琴乃ならきっと大丈夫だと思うわ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 141.8252532643,
      "endTime": 149.98126227080002,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_studentcouncilroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "seitokai",
      "startTime": 150.1822371802
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui Tendo",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2510_01_05/sud_vo_adv_event_2510_01_05-rui003.m4a",
      "text": "……それに、このミュージカルは\n優が学校のみんなのために書き上げたものなの",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 150.1822371802,
      "endTime": 156.7822373709,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui Tendo",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2510_01_05/sud_vo_adv_event_2510_01_05-rui004.m4a",
      "text": "見た人が学校に来て良かったって……みんな学校の\n主人公なんだって思えるように心をこめて",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 156.9832122804,
      "endTime": 165.7079578401,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_studentcouncilroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "seitokai",
      "startTime": 166.0422793072
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui Tendo",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
